OL,6,FITV News Meridian's Malcom Shaw has
OL,7,Fbeen with Kent Police to find out
OL,8,Fabout the arrests made under Operation
OL,9,FLimit
OL,11,FDrink and drug driving in Kent has led
OL,12,Fto more than 100 arrests so far this
OL,13,Fmonth, local police say.
OL,15,FKent Police have been taking part in a
OL,16,Fnational initiative called Operation
OL,17,FLimit, which aims to raise awareness
OL,18,Fof the danger of drink-and-drug
OL,19,Fdriving, and reduce the number of
OL,20,Fpeople killed and seriously injured in
OL,21,Froad traffic incidents.
