OL,3,CChristmas drink and drug driving
OL,4,Ccampaign: 100 arrests
OL,6,FDuring the month of December, more
OL,7,Fpeople are out celebrating, therefore
OL,8,Fpolice want to remind drivers of the
OL,9,Fconsequences of being over the limit,
OL,10,Fwhich can include a fine, driving ban,
OL,11,Fand a criminal conviction.
OL,13,FDuring the crackdown, police have been
OL,14,Frandomly pulling people over,
OL,15,Fbreathalysing the drivers for alcohol
OL,16,Fthen testing for drugs like cannabis
OL,17,Fand cocaine.
