OL,6,FThey say that driving under the
OL,7,Finfluence of drink or drugs is one of
OL,8,Fthe 'fatal factors' that put vehicles
OL,9,Fowners at most risk.
OL,11,FKent Police also say that people are
OL,12,Fup to sixteen times more likely to be
OL,13,Finvolved in a crash causing a death or
OL,14,Fserious injury, under the influence.
OL,16,FScores of drivers have already been
OL,17,Farrested, including a 19-year old
OL,18,FMargate man arrested on Beacon Road,
OL,19,FBroadstairs for testing positive for
OL,20,Ftraces of cannabis and cocaine, after
OL,21,Fdriving into a parked vehicle.
