OL,6,FThey say that he 'failed a roadside
OL,7,Fbreath test and was arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of driving whilst over the
OL,9,Flegal limit for alcohol. He was later
OL,10,Freleased on bail pending further
OL,11,Fenquiries.'
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV News Meridian, Chief
OL,14,FInspector Craig West, who is the Head
OL,15,Fof Roads Policing at Kent Police,
OL,16,Fwarned people against drink and drug
OL,17,Fdriving.
OL,19,FHe said: "Simply do not take the risk;
OL,20,Fit is selfish and unnecessary."
