OL,6,F"You can order a taxi, ask a friend to
OL,7,Fgive you a lift or a member of your
OL,8,Ffamily, or you can simply walk home."
OL,10,F"It is not worth the risk. If you get
OL,11,Fbehind the wheel of a car whilst you
OL,12,Fare impaired from alcohol or drugs,
OL,13,Fexpect to get stopped by police,
OL,14,Ftested and expect to be arrested."
